import Navbar from "./navbar"
import About from "./pages/About"
import Blogs from "./pages/Blogs"
import Home from "./pages/Home"
import "./styles.css"
export default function App() {
  
  let Component
  switch (window.location.pathname) {
    case "/":
    Component= <Home /> 
    break
      case "/blogs":
        Component= <Blogs /> 
        break
        case "/about":
          Component= <About /> 
          break
  }
  
  
  return(
    <>
    <Navbar />

    </>
  )
}
